sections.heading: deed; reconveyance; beneficiary's obligation and liability
sections.text: Section 76-2803 shall govern the beneficiary's obligation to record or cause to be recorded a deed of reconveyance and the liability of the beneficiary for failure to timely record or cause to be recorded a deed of reconveyance.SourceLaws 19
